channel.title: [Delta] Webclient
channel.description:
I may me misunderstanding the guides, but they all say stuff about downloading cache and whatnot. The client I use just has everything right in the client, it downloads nothing. I don't have a custom cache (it's just a plain old 377).
Is there a way to make a webclient without it downloading cache? I tried doing the tutorials, skipping the parts with the cache (so pretty much the cache is in the .jar with the client), but it just does the Java loading thing (for quite awhile) and then errors (client.class not found).
